{"title":"transforms","uid":"9e62d0a444a3b1ec871807663ed3323c","slug":"transforms","date":"2021-09-22T02:17:13.000Z","updated":"2021-09-22T02:17:56.086Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/transforms.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://cjpnice-picture.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/202109162005428.png","content":"<h1 id=\"pytorch入门\"><a href=\"#pytorch入门\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"pytorch入门\"></a>pytorch入门</h1><h2 id=\"引入包\"><a href=\"#引入包\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"引入包\"></a>引入包</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-python\" data-language=\"python\"><code class=\"language-python\">from torchvision import  transforms</code></pre>\n\n<h2 id=\"ToTensor\"><a href=\"#ToTensor\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"ToTensor\"></a>ToTensor</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-python\" data-language=\"python\"><code class=\"language-python\">img_path &#x3D; &quot;img&#x2F;1.jpg&quot;\nimg &#x3D; Image.open(img_path)\ntensor_trans &#x3D; transforms.ToTensor()\ntensor_img &#x3D; tensor_trans(img)\nprint(tensor_img.data)</code></pre>\n\n<h2 id=\"Resize\"><a href=\"#Resize\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Resize\"></a>Resize</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-python\" data-language=\"python\"><code class=\"language-python\">trans_resize &#x3D; transforms.Resize((960,1080))\nimg_resize &#x3D; trans_resize(tensor_img)\nprint(img_resize.size())</code></pre>\n\n<h2 id=\"Compose\"><a href=\"#Compose\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Compose\"></a>Compose</h2><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z